{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2aa8a605f1","title":"康生对宁夏军区的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c7a610318","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"2aa8a605f1","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"朱声达","id":"1f87830db4","type":"人物"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6e9565211e","type":"title","text":"康生对宁夏军区的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"417e8ac5ac","type":"paragraph","text":"（宁夏军区副司令员张怀礼同志传达）","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90aced3548","type":"paragraph","text":"一、筹备处派代表去北京谈判，不是搞重庆谈判，是受教育。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8886642dd","type":"paragraph","text":"二、加强宣传，报纸、电台、宣传车，对中央首长关于宁夏问题的谈话、兰州军区公告，要反复宣传，把有线广播搞起来（特别是电台有线广播）。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed69a40872","type":"paragraph","text":"三、不要抓头头，抓来要放。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74f2cedb76","type":"paragraph","text":"四、适当的分发武器，要武装造反派，如果他们对银川进行反扑，坚决自卫。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc937c1421","type":"paragraph","text":"五、筹备处破坏铁路，康老很生气，把朱声达叫去训一顿。这是反革命事件。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"54dce89d68","type":"paragraph","text":"六、第三势力对自己参加谈判的代表数量少，他们很有意见，中央说可以考虑。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ce8d65346","type":"paragraph","text":"七、继续用飞机散发传单。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2aa8a605f1","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}